<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l2">vnd hauptman cʒu Tachawe </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_452_r1l3"><expan>Ervvirdig<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vns ewr ervvirdıkeit nehſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l4"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> guten willen / den Jr gen vns / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l5">vnd den ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> habt wol cʒu verſteen <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / Alſo haben ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l6">etlich <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kaufflewte auf ſölchen troſt etvvieuil </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l7">hab vnd kauffmanſchaft hinein gen Beheim geſchickt / dıe biſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l8">gen Tachaw kumen iſt / Als vns ~ die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> geſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l9">ſchıcken darümb cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Recken <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l10">mit ew cʒu reden vvie dıeſelb hab vnd kauffmanſchaft fürbaʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l11">kumen vnd <expan>ſich<ex>er</ex></expan> geleytet werden müg / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / vvaʒ der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l12"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> von <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kaufflewte vnd <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> habe vvegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l14">an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade 
<del rend="strikethrough">brınge </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_452_r1l13">werb </ab></add> / daʒ Jr Jn darynne <expan>gütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l15">auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hilff <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd ernſt darcʒu tun wöllet / daʒ dieſelb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l16">hab durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gepiete ſicher geleẏtet werde Als vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l17">des wol <expan>getr<ex>awen</ex></expan> / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir vmb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>Erwirdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıene<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_452" id="225v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Sulco, <expan>probst<ex>en</ex></expan> czu
                        Chotischaw und hauptman czu Tachawe </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erwirdig<ex>er</ex></expan> und lieber
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als uns ewr
                                                erwirdikeit nehst
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> guten willen, den ir
                                                gen uns, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat und den
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> habt, wol czu
                                                versteen <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, also
                                                haben etlich <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kaufflewte auf
                                                sölchen trost etwievil hab und kauffmanschaft hinein
                                                gen Beheim geschickt, die bisz gen Tachaw kumen ist,
                                                als uns die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gesagt
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n;</expan> und schicken darümb
                                                czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                                                  <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Recken,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burger, mit ew czu
                                                reden, wie dieselb hab und kauffmanschaft fürbaz
                                                kumen und <expan>sich<ex>er</ex></expan> geleytet
                                                werden müg. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz
                                                der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> von
                                                  <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kaufflewte und
                                                  <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> habe wegen an
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade <add>werb,</add>
                                                daz ir in darynne <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> und auch
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hilff,
                                                  <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und ernst darczu
                                                tun wöllet, daz dieselb hab durch
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gepiete sicher
                                                geleytet werde, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> des wol
                                                  <expan>getr<ex>awen.</ex></expan> Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir umb
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>diene<ex>n</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
